    "description": "“Mirror”的世界里出现了危机！为了自己心中坚持的正义，主角们开始混战。<br>以名为“可爱”的正义，代表你喜欢的角色开始战斗吧！<br><br>迷你游戏合集《Mirror Party》全新登场！内置4款迷你游戏， 支持多人联机同乐。（<strong>未来将持续更新</strong>）<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【游戏内容】</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787820/extras/84ecead6ea46c9637e8fed6c544818e5.poster.avif?t=1755198468\" width=616 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787820/extras/84ecead6ea46c9637e8fed6c544818e5.webm?t=1755198468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787820/extras/84ecead6ea46c9637e8fed6c544818e5.mp4?t=1755198468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><li>坦克对决：任何人都无法阻挡坦克的前进......  ！有敌军正在接近！埋伏还是突击？不惧炮火的人才能获得最后的胜利。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787820/extras/61e13e26da898c99a6d16046210e7b08.poster.avif?t=1755198468\" width=616 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787820/extras/61e13e26da898c99a6d16046210e7b08.webm?t=1755198468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787820/extras/61e13e26da898c99a6d16046210e7b08.mp4?t=1755198468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>莉娅的秘密房间：莉娅似乎需要一个帮手，来收集房间内各种遗失的道具。她从不吝啬奖励他人，哪怕是...奖励自己？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787820/extras/a4616f3790484660293d15f731957692.poster.avif?t=1755198468\" width=616 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787820/extras/a4616f3790484660293d15f731957692.webm?t=1755198468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787820/extras/a4616f3790484660293d15f731957692.mp4?t=1755198468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>火球战争：躲避，进攻，看谁能坚持到最后，或许……你还需要一些小小的帮助？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787820/extras/ef5e85dda7d7d1af497c8fb845646557.poster.avif?t=1755198468\" width=616 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787820/extras/ef5e85dda7d7d1af497c8fb845646557.webm?t=1755198468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787820/extras/ef5e85dda7d7d1af497c8fb845646557.mp4?t=1755198468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>疯狂农场：农场里真是乱套了，快使用南瓜将他们捕获起来吧。瞄准、射击，偶尔还会有一些水果的帮助。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【扭蛋系统】</h2>突然出现了奇怪的东西！这是...“扭蛋币”？带去扭蛋机那里试一试吧，好像能抽出各种有趣的收集品。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787820/extras/35f890c852854dea172c6c7014ffa050.poster.avif?t=1755198468\" width=616 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787820/extras/35f890c852854dea172c6c7014ffa050.webm?t=1755198468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787820/extras/35f890c852854dea172c6c7014ffa050.mp4?t=1755198468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>通过游玩小游戏获取扭蛋币，消耗扭蛋币即可在扭蛋机里抽取收集品。EA阶段可获得100+张Cosplay写真/视频，100+张游戏原画/设定集，另外还有角色头像、音乐OST、人声曲片段......并且扭蛋系统奖池将跟随开发进度持续更新，正式版预计将有1000+件物品等你来收集！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【游戏特色】</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>可爱的Q版3D角色形象<br></li><li>丰富的游戏类型<br></li><li>300+件收集品的扭蛋收集系统（正式版超过1000件）<br></li><li>支持多人联机游玩</li></ul>",
